My teacher told me to do a couple exercises on my instrument that she GUARANTEED would get me to my goals if I did them religiously but I've been doing them and I'm still not improving. I'm VERY worried I won't be ready by the time of the audition, which would be really embarrassing because a lot of people think I'm really really good even though I'm not. I really need some advice.
